text: Gone to Coney Island and Booming Business is a 1910 American silent comedy movie.GONE TO CONEY ISLAND It stars Anna Rosemond, Frank H. Crane, and Violet Heming. ==Plot== The movie tells about a maid named Kate who works at Mrs. Green's house. Her lover works in Coney Island and asks to leave the family and get a job as a salesman, but Mrs. Green is against it. ==References== Category:1910 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American silent movies
title: Gone to Coney Island and Booming Business
